["Xiguit District or Shiguai District (Mongolian: \u1830\u1822\u182d\u1824\u1836\u1822\u1832\u1824  \u1832\u1823\u182d\u1823\u1837\u1822\u182d  Si\u0263uyitu to\u0263ori\u0263, \u0428\u0438\u0433\u0443\u0430\u0439 \u0442\u043e\u0439\u0440\u043e\u0433; simplified Chinese: \u77f3\u62d0\u533a ; traditional Chinese: \u77f3\u62d0\u5340 ; pinyin: Sh\u00edgu\u01cei Q\u016b ) is an outlying district of Baotou, the largest city of Inner Mongolia, People's Republic of China.","The district is home to Badekar Monastery and the national park that surrounds it.[1]","This Inner Mongolia location article is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it."]